---
layout: base
title: Articles
description: Practical language-learning activities and frameworks.
permalink: /articles/
---

<h1>Articles</h1>
<p class="lede">Practical language-learning activities and frameworks you can use with any language.</p>

{% for section in collections.articleSections %}
  <section class="article-section">
    <h2>{{ section.title }}</h2>
    <div class="article-list">
      {% for item in section.items %}
        <article class="article-list-item">
          <h3 class="article-list-title"><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.navTitle or item.data.title }}</a></h3>
          {% if item.data.summary %}
            <p class="article-list-description">{{ item.data.summary }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
{% endfor %}
